cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CE, cs.NE, cs.SI

The paper proposes a machine learning model that combines physics-based models and recurrent neural networks to improve the modeling of physical processes. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The application of the proposed methodology is in simulating lake temperature profiles, which falls under the category of computational engineering (cs.CE) and natural environment (cs.NE). Finally, the paper discusses the potential applicability of the proposed methodology in a range of scientific and engineering disciplines, which falls under the category of scientific computing (cs.SI).
